short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Describe your dev environment as code and get fully prebuilt dev environments for any GitLab, GitHub and Bitbucket project.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: DevSpaces allows developers to launch github code in a container based IDE and get started with developing code in seconds. No more downloading code to the local machine and setting up a local environment to get started.
